---
import PageLayout from "../components/PageLayout.astro";
import "../sass/pages/dj.scss";
---

<PageLayout
    title="DJ PAPI"
    subtitle="International DJ"
    description="DJ portfolio by Aayan Shaikh - When a dancer hijacks the DJ booth"
>
    <p>
        If you've ever wondered what happens when a dancer hijacks the DJ booth,
        wonder no more. As the resident DJ at <strong>Cobbler and Crew</strong> (India's
        #2 bar—my mom's still not impressed), I specialize in mixing genres that
        keep your feet moving and your Fitbit confused.
    </p>

    <div class="genres-grid">
        <div class="genre-card">🎵 Kizomba</div>
        <div class="genre-card">💃 Bachata</div>
        <div class="genre-card">🕺 Salsa</div>
        <div class="genre-card">🕰️ Retro</div>
        <div class="genre-card">✨ Disco</div>
        <div class="genre-card">🏠 House</div>
        <div class="genre-card">🎆 EDM</div>
        <div class="genre-card">📻 Commercial</div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Performance Highlights</h2>
        <div class="grid-2">
            <div class="card highlight-card">
                <h3>🎤 Opened For</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Karan Kanchan</li>
                    <li>The Yellow Diary</li>
                    <li>SuReal</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="card highlight-card">
                <h3>🏢 Venues</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>High Spirits</li>
                    <li>FREQ</li>
                    <li>Elephant and Co</li>
                    <li>QORA</li>
                    <li>Symbiosis</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>My Secret Sauce</h2>
        <div class="grid-auto">
            <div class="card">
                <span class="emoji">👂</span>
                <p>A dancer's ear for rhythm</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <span class="emoji">💿</span>
                <p>A crate of vinyl classics</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <span class="emoji">🚫</span>
                <p>Refusal to play "Despacito" more than twice a night</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="closing-note">
        After my set, you'll usually find me at the bar, pretending to
        understand wine lists and chatting with anyone who'll listen.
    </p>
</PageLayout>
